  ;; ============================================================
  ;; DESIGN NOTES
  ;; ============================================================
  ;; GM 8.0 body is 12.8x5.8mm -- fits within the 54mm board with
  ;; some margin. Verify no overlap with H1/H2 mount holes.
  ;; Blue Dot body ~8.75mm -- positioned at board edge X=+-24mm,
  ;; plunger protrudes slightly outside board edge through top_frame cutout.
  ;; Check top_frame side cutout size accommodates Blue Dot body (update
  ;; top_side_sw_w/top_side_sw_h in params.scad if needed).
  ;; NC pins on GM 8.0 left floating (unconnected).

)
